    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of normal road use, while the interior remains in great shape with some light wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it is very sound, drives smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as they should. It\u2019s a reliable choice for someone looking for a solid car that has been cared for over the years.",
