    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, reflecting a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. From the pristine interior appointments to the mirror-finish exterior, every detail affirms its status as a collector-grade acquisition. This is an uncompromising choice for the individual who demands peak automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
